para_trans: Reference: - Government Decision, serial number, d. 23.12.2024.
Mr. Jaykumar Nayankumar Jitendra Singh Rawal, Hon'ble Minister at Malabar Hill, Mumbai
The government bungalow "Chitrakoot" was allotted as per the relevant government decision. Instead, the government has now decided to allot them a bungalow called "Parnakuti" in Malabar Hill.
Fifteen Residences allotted to the Hon'ble Minister after he demits office.
It will be mandatory to vacate within a period of days.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
